        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Veterans and Consumers Fair Credit Act </b></p> <p>This bill applies certain military consumer credit protections to all consumers. Specifically, the bill caps the interest rate on extensions of consumer credit at 36%. </p>]]>
        </text>
